timeshift (1.5.1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Added option to install bootloader on partition VBR

  * Added option to skip bootloader installation

  * Fixed: Enabling automatic snapshots removes existing cron jobs

  * Fixed an issue where the backup device status was not detected correctly
  
  * Backup jobs now run at the minimum backup interval selected by user

  * Use regular expression matching for searching crontab entries
  
  * Various fixes and improvements
  
 -- Tony George <tony.george.kol@gmail.com>  Sun, 17 Aug 2014 11:00:00 +0530
